# 🎓 Students Grading System

## 📌 Overview
A simple web app that allows teachers or students to calculate grades based on marks and display results in a table format.

## 🧠 Features
- Enter student name and marks
- Automatically calculate grade
- Display all results neatly in a table

## ⚙️ Technologies Used
- HTML  
- CSS  
- JavaScript  

## 🚀 Deployment
This project is deployed via **GitHub Pages**.

## 🔗 Live Demo
